
Note for translators of the pot files:
======================================

Please make a copy of the pot file renaming it to reflect the language it is
being translated in to. For example, for a German translation of rs274_err.pot,
your working file would be de_rs274_err.po - If the file does not exist within
the CVS repository, then feel free to create one from a *.pot template.


Note for translators of the .msg files (flo-h's method):
========================================================

(A better way is perhaps only publishing the po files here and creating the msg files by makefile)
Replace all de's with your language identifier.

1. Create a empty .pot file with all existing translations (creates messages.po):
cd ~/emc2/tcl
xgettext tkemc.tcl mini.tcl bin/emccalib.tcl bin/emcdebug.tcl bin/emclog.tcl bin/emctesting.tcl bin/emctuning.tcl bin/genedit.tcl bin/pickconfig.tcl bin/tkbackplot.tcl bin/tkio.tcl bin/halconfig.tcl bin/halshow.tcl scripts/balloon.tcl scripts/emchelp.tcl scripts/Set_Coordinates.tcl (and add other files with translations)

2. merge the .po file with the existing translations
msgmerge ../src/po/de_msg.po messages.po > de_new_msg.po

3. Edit the new .po file (etc. with poedit)
poedit de_new_msg.po

4. create a .msg file from the .po file
msgfmt --tcl -l de -d ./ de_new_msg.po
mv de.msg ../src/po/

5. Replace the old .po file
mv de_new_msg.po ../src/po/de_msg.po

6. Update the two files
cvs commit ../src/po/de.msg ../src/po/de_msg.po


Convertion of existing .msg files to .po files
----------------------------------------------
1. Open the file withe an Editor (KEdit)
2. Delete head an comments
3. Delete multiple entrys
4. Replace [::msgcat::mcset de] with [msgid] (change language identifier like "de" with the one in your file)
5. Replace [" "] with [" msgstr "]
6. Add head (like this):

# This file provides german translations for EMC2
# Copyright (C) 2005 THE PACKAGE'S COPYRIGHT HOLDER
# This file is distributed under the same license as the EMC2 package
# Your Name <Your.Mail@domain.tld>, 01.Jan.2006
#
msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: EMC2\n"
"Report-Msgid-Bugs-To: \n"
"POT-Creation-Date: 2006-03-26 01:03+0100\n"
"PO-Revision-Date: 2006-03-26 01:10+0100\n"
"Last-Translator: This is automatically changeg by POEdit <i@ii.ii>\n"
"Language-Team: EMC LOCALIZATION TEAM <emc-developers@lists.sourceforge.net>\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"

7. Thats it